@startuml
title Lab 6 Part 2 - Analogue Conditioning Pipeline
left to right direction

rectangle "Raw value\n(NTC or DHT11)" as RAW
rectangle "Saturation\nClamp to [-20, 80] C" as SAT
rectangle "Median filter\n3 samples" as MED
rectangle "Weighted average\n4 samples\n50,25,15,10" as WAV
rectangle "Filtered value" as FILT
rectangle "Optional alert\nvalidation" as THR
rectangle "LCD / STDIO /\nLEDs / buzzer" as OUT

RAW --> SAT
SAT --> MED
MED --> WAV
WAV --> FILT
FILT --> THR
THR --> OUT

note bottom of MED
Rejects isolated spikes
end note

note bottom of WAV
Smooths the recent history
end note

@enduml
